Revision history for Shaderc

v2016.0-dev 2016-05-19

 - Adds v<year>.<index> versioning, with "-dev" indicating
   work in progress.  The intent is to more easly report
   and summarize functionality when Shaderc is incorporated
   in downstream projects.

 - Summary of functionality (See the README.md for more):
   - Compiles GLSL to SPIR-V binary through both command line and API calls
   - Supports #include
   - Supports compiling GLSL to SPIR-V assembly code
   - Supports compiling SPIR-V assembly code to SPIR-V binary
   - Supports OpenGL, OpenGL Compatible and Vulkan semantics
   - Supports user-defined macros
   - Supports dependency information dumping
